class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ffa1665702662616.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ffa1665702662616.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ffa1665702662616.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ffa1665702662616\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                                \n Type\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Type of menu item.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ffa1665702662616__p_d110234e1_d110235e1_d110236e1\">The available types of menu items depend on the type of menu. For example, a menu bar can only included separators and references to drop-down menus, whereas a drop-down menu can also include menu options and references to other menus.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Types of Menu Items</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__1\"> Item type </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__2\">Available In</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__3\">Triggers</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__4\"> Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__1\"> Menu Option</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__2\">Drop-down<p class=\"p\">Pop-up</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__3\">\n                                       preDisplay\n                                       <p class=\"p\">select</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__4\">Performs an action, such as activating a\n\t\t\t\t form or structure editor function.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__1\"> Dynamic Menu</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__2\">Drop-down<p class=\"p\">Pop-up</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__3\">\n                                       preDisplay\n                                       <p class=\"p\">select</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__4\">Placeholder where additional menu items\n\t\t\t\t can be inserted at runtime by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$inlinemenu</span> ProcScript statements in the\n\t\t\t\t preDisplay trigger.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__1\"> Cascaded Menu</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__2\">Drop-down<p class=\"p\">Pop-up</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__3\">\n                                       preDisplay\n                                      </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__4\"> References a drop-down menu, displaying\n\t\t\t\t its contents as a separate menu cascading from the current menu.<p class=\"p\">Use a cascading menu to include additional\n\t\t\t\t items in a menu that would otherwise cause the menu to be too long.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">For usability, don't define more than\n\t\t\t\t three levels of cascading menus.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__1\"> Included Menu </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__2\">Drop-down<p class=\"p\">Pop-up</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__4\">References a drop-down menu, copying its\n\t\t\t\t contents into the current menu during compilation. Use included menus to avoid duplicating menu\n\t\t\t\t item definitions.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__1\"> Separator </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__2\">Drop-down<p class=\"p\">Pop-up</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__3\">\n                                       preDisplay\n                                      </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__4\">Horizontal dividing line used to separate\n\t\t\t\t groups of related items. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__1\"> Drop-down Menu </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__2\">Menu Bar</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__3\">\n                                       preDisplay\n                                      </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__4\">References a drop-down menu. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__1\"> Right Align Marker </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__2\">Menu Bar</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__3\">\n                                       preDisplay\n                                      </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ffa1665702662616__table_d12986e1_d12987e1_d12988e1__entry__4\">Causes subsequent items to be displayed on\n\t\t\t\t the right side of the application window. <p class=\"p\">Only one of these should or needs to be\n\t\t\t\t present in a menu bar.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527474\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527474\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Type Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Version: Use up/down arrow keys to navigate, Esc to collapse. Rocket Uniface Library 10.4 Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.0 Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.1 Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.1 Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.0 Reflection Desktop User Guide (German) Secure Host Access FTP Client User Guide (German) Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.0 Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.0 Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.1 Reflection FTP Scripting (German) V21.1 Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.1 Rocket Uniface Library 10.4 Rocket Uniface Library 10.4 Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.0 Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.1 Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.1 Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.0 Reflection Desktop User Guide (German) Secure Host Access FTP Client User Guide (German) Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.0 Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.0 Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.1 Reflection FTP Scripting (German) V21.1 Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.1 Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Type Type of menu item. The available types of menu items depend on the type of menu. For example, a menu bar can only included separators and references to drop-down menus, whereas a drop-down menu can also include menu options and references to other menus. Table 1. Types of Menu Items Item type Available In Triggers Description Menu Option Drop-down Pop-up preDisplay select Performs an action, such as activating a form or structure editor function. Dynamic Menu Drop-down Pop-up preDisplay select Placeholder where additional menu items can be inserted at runtime by $inlinemenu ProcScript statements in the preDisplay trigger. Cascaded Menu Drop-down Pop-up preDisplay References a drop-down menu, displaying its contents as a separate menu cascading from the current menu. Use a cascading menu to include additional items in a menu that would otherwise cause the menu to be too long. For usability, don't define more than three levels of cascading menus. Included Menu Drop-down Pop-up None References a drop-down menu, copying its contents into the current menu during compilation. Use included menus to avoid duplicating menu item definitions. Separator Drop-down Pop-up preDisplay Horizontal dividing line used to separate groups of related items. Drop-down Menu Menu Bar preDisplay References a drop-down menu. Right Align Marker Menu Bar preDisplay Causes subsequent items to be displayed on the right side of the application window. Only one of these should or needs to be present in a menu bar. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}